{"word":"G1799 - ἐνώπιον - enṓpion - en-o'-pee-on - Before","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐνώπιον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">enṓpion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en-o'-pee-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Before</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Preposition / முன்னிடைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"முன்பாக, முன்னே, பார்வையில் - இடைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"one who is in sight"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a compound of <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and a derivation of <a href=\"#/G3700 - ὀπτάνομαι - optánomai - op-tan'-om-ahee/3700\">G3700</a>; <i>in</i> the <i>face</i> of (literally or figuratively): - before, in the presence (sight) of, to.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}